trans-unit.source: UCI Bike Rental dataset that is based on real data from Capital Bikeshare company that maintains a bike rental network in Washington DC.
trans-unit.target: UCI Bike Rental dataset that is based on real data from Capital Bikeshare company that maintains a bike rental network in Washington DC.

trans-unit.source: The dataset has one row for each hour of each day in 2011 and 2012, for a total of 17,379 rows.
trans-unit.target: The dataset has one row for each hour of each day in 2011 and 2012, for a total of 17,379 rows.

trans-unit.source: The range of hourly bike rentals is from 1 to 977.
